Chaotic Arrow
/fx burn-magic @{target|token_id}
!roll20AM --audio,play,nomenu|arrow
@{Eladrin Archer|wtype}&{template:npcfullatk} {{attack=1}} {{damage=1}} {{dmg1flag=1}} {{dmg2flag=1}}  @{Eladrin Archer|npc_name_flag} {{rname=Chaotic Arrow}} {{r1=[[@{Eladrin Archer|d20}+(6+0)]]}} @{Eladrin Archer|rtype}+(6+0)]]}} {{dmg1=[[1d8 + 4+0]]}} {{dmg1type=piercing}} {{dmg2=[[2d8+0]]}} {{dmg2type=[[1t[Chaos-Bolt]]]}} {{crit1=[[1d8+0]]}} {{crit2=[[2d8+0]]}} {{Modifier|1t[Random-Table-Effect-Type]}} {{description=The arrowhead carries with it a warbling mass of chaotic energy. On a hit, the target takes an additional 2d8 of a random damage type. 

If you roll the same number on both d8s, the chaotic energy leaps from the target to a different creature of your choice within 30 feet of it. Make a new ranged attack roll against the new target, and make a new damage roll, which could cause the chaotic energy to leap again. If there is no target within 30' the bolt dissipates.
}} @{Eladrin Archer|charname_output}


